|:-------|:--------:|:----:|:-----------:|
| Training Time | 100% | 50-70% | **30-50% faster** |
| Compute Cost | 100% | 50-70% | **30-50% cheaper** |
| Final Loss | $\ell^*$ | $\leq \ell^*$ | Equal or better |

